## NAMING CONVENTION

### IO Layer (Message Movers)
- Format: io.{channel}.{verb}
- Channels: mq, tg, http, fs
- Verbs: publish, consume, ingress, egress, watch, drop

### OPS Layer (Side Effects)
- Format: ops.{runtime_or_domain}.{verb}
- Runtimes: python, shell, ssh, db, fs
- Verbs: exec, query, migrate, write, read

## ADAPTER STRUCTURE

Every adapter exposes 3 files:
- spec.ref (contract - immutable)
- status.ref (health snapshot - overwrite allowed)
- run.{ex|rs|py|sh} (implementation)

